{"tid":2200373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲搜新華社職員住所 沒收器材","createTime":"2020-09-13T02:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T05:26:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3e454d178aa965c8d6c08fb43d41b053c0377342","tid":2200373,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T02:38:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200913/MV7CMKDOC5HGXDH27NHMA3LINU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200913%2FMV7CMKDOC5HGXDH27NHMA3LINU%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=25d5053a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200913%2FMV7CMKDOC5HGXDH27NHMA3LINU%2F&h=584c2678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200913/MV7CMKDOC5HGXDH27NHMA3LINU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n澳洲搜新華社職員住所 沒收器材<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q7cyRN7hOmvLjKN9qF5JvmxvprA=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XPETIHQOUJD5PIO2WNUEQ3VGV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ7cyRN7hOmvLjKN9qF5JvmxvprA%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXPETIHQOUJD5PIO2WNUEQ3VGV4.jpg&h=0a6346e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■兩名澳洲記者早前撤離中國。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n中澳關係惡化，在中國官媒工作的澳洲華裔記者成蕾早前被中國扣留，兩名駐華澳洲記者再被約談，引來澳洲官方批評。中方媒體之後又稱澳洲6月也曾搜查多名中國媒體駐澳洲記者住所，涉事的新華社和中新社發聲明，指記者住所被闖入並粗暴搜查，表示強烈譴責和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新華社稱「長期秉持客觀公正」<br />\n<br />\n新華社前日發聲明指，今年6月26日，澳方在沒有任何證據的情形下，搜查中國媒體駐澳記者，又扣押採訪和發稿設備，新華社形容澳方行徑粗暴、蠻橫無理，充份暴露了澳方個別部門和官員的冷戰思維和政治偏見，嚴重干擾中澳兩國正常的人文交流。<br />\n<br />\n中新社昨聲明指，澳方安。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新華社和中新社的聲明強調，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新華社"},{"pid":"72cae56d49fc82b7aa1bdf11fa4121b24c902634","tid":2200373,"uid":286897,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adbe0048f2583506336d8a79d66cd41aba089dc4","tid":2200373,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"外交對等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那搞民主國家，人地唔一定還拖<br />\n但支那狗比人搞 就一定咬番人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce96047be06e98c88525894b5cba94e2d8a0f56","tid":2200373,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:10:46.000Z","msg":"打仗啦打仗啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cd7dd24969fad156c16aa03054ec9d34be6b73","tid":2200373,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe599dfd1a029d3933ccdc4a116b843d3d7afb9","tid":2200373,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"要用刑逼供"},{"pid":"8e758e86095371503b352eb445ecaf0e370cca8d","tid":2200373,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:16:06.000Z","msg":"澳洲只是依法辦事"},{"pid":"00ac6e678ae2b1f7c254b411373ffccbf80811bd","tid":2200373,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T03:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa61d883d9fc2f279c9b61146e5ead0590d3b65d","tid":2200373,"uid":103050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-1